replies.body: Its probability is low, but it definitely isn't impossible.

FNC has a good chance of getting to finals.  After watching SKT dismantle AHQ in 3 games like they did I don't see OG getting past them.  It would be awesome to see as I really like the EU teams ( I'm a C9 fan for life ) since my NA teams dropped the ball in groups.  

It's not impossible but the stars have to align for OG to get past SKT.  I predict an SKT vs FNC finals.
SKT could play worse next week you never know.
